      "description": "This F87 M2 features the N55 3.0L inline-six with TwinPower Turbo technology, delivering 365 hp and 343 lb-ft of torque. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and an Active M Differential for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis maintains its rigidity with forged aluminum components and a track-tuned suspension geometry. This example has been meticulously serviced, ensuring the VANOS system and cooling circuit are in prime operational state. Minor cosmetic wear consistent with mileage, but mechanically robust with linear power delivery and precise turn-in.",
